➜老全兴浇出新玫瑰
http://www.sohu.com/a/425896764_114731	1326
<p>原标题：老全兴浇出新玫瑰 </p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201020/de6f34776c0c4e2f92d2bf056db63190.jpeg" /></p>
